Title: Found Local Friend in UAE
DateModified: '2019-03-04'
DatePublished: '2019-03-04'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/found-local-friend-in-uae
SetInCountry: United Arab Emirates
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Prince Malhi
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "Last year in Jan. 2018 i was travelling to UAE. When i reached on Airport then\
  \ i took a Cab and  suddenly i left my Mobile in Cab. I reached at hotel and suddenly\
  \ i Remember about my mobile.\nI went to nearest Police Station to do complaint\
  \ about lost Mobile. After this i saw the Cab driver same before one at front of\
  \ the hotel. He was local citizen and he return my mobile to Me. I was shocked and\
  \ got my mobile.I was very Thankful.I was a kind & Honest man. He also became my\
  \ friend too. He took me for Outing in UAE. We enjoyed alot and now he is my one\
  \ of the best Friend overthere.\nIt was a great Journey for Me. I Want to Go again\
  \ in UAE.\nI travelled in 2 or more counties and I found In all countries , all\
  \ people are same. Alot people are very helpful ,Honest and kind. In travelling\
  \ we learn alot things and we make friends in different counties.\n Thanks For Read\
  \ my Story.\nPrince Malhi"
